{"tid":1512671,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"航空業係未做左condom？？","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:20:59.000Z","uid":187578,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"52246cffa97b0b03534c725d36606142e88daba1","tid":1512671,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"佢地為香港發聲 罷工，幫手宣傳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但依家呢？佢地有事我地有冇幫拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日國泰集會完全唔夠多人知呀！！！</span></strong>大家都剩係推metoo集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家兩個一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去完國泰再去metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />航空業界面對梗<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>白色恐怖</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連工都不保<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果佢地出事，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>以後只會更少人願意發聲</strong></span> 甚至九月罷工都唔會搞得成！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係講好咗一方有難 八方支援嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>航空業界唔係condom！大家幫手call馬！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日有兩個集會<br />\n今日有兩個集會<br />\n今日有兩個集會</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCctVsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCctVsy.jpg&h=fd9507a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JGnfsA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JGnfsA.jpg&h=cf03adf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1339b24db23b2a7fb89912bfd59b81db9474d67","tid":1512671,"uid":187578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03: